# Production-only env (loaded by Vite on `vite build`, mode=production).
# SECRETS NEVER GO HERE - this file is committed. Public build flags only.
# Secrets stay in Vercel env vars / the gitignored .env(.local).
#
# Entry gate: premium multilingual intro overlay on the homepage ("/").
# "on" activates it (Vite swaps %VITE_ENTRY_GATE% in index.html + keeps the
# gate chunk). Visitors can skip with ?gate=0.
VITE_ENTRY_GATE="on"
